From: Random Developer <random-dev@example.com>
Date: Tue, 1 May 2026 09:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Comment out inline definition of msg_init_ns in ipc/util.h to avoid redefinition conflict

This patch comments out the inline definition of msg_init_ns in ipc/util.h to resolve the redefinition conflict with the full function definition in ipc/msg.c.

---
 ipc/util.h | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/ipc/util.h b/ipc/util.h
index 1234567..89abcdef 100644
--- a/ipc/util.h
+++ b/ipc/util.h
@@ -74,7 +74,7 @@
  * Function declarations and other definitions
  */
 
- static inline void msg_init_ns(struct ipc_namespace *ns) { }
+ // static inline void msg_init_ns(struct ipc_namespace *ns) { }
 
